Averaged previous February measurement according to February 2020 visit MGH (7.896m). Used data points from 2010, 2012, 2015 and 2016 February visits. Average february visit is on the 17th and averaging discharge of 2.285 m3/s. If i used all data points including march/april visits, the average discharge is 2.074 m3/s, close enough to the February average so I decided to just use the February visits for consistency.
